	<td class="alt2" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>I think simply from the number of guilds and raids that use LFG to form up, that it must have some merit for getting things moving quickly and easily. Everybody has their own style for forming raids, my previous guild used LFG all the time and we can get formed and pulling in 15 minutes from raid called. <br />
<br />
Yes I often get 4 or 5 tells when LFG for a raid, a simple, "sorry, raiding" takes care of it. If I have to go AFK briefly it goes in my AFK message.</p>
	
	
	
